events.text: The Trailblazers traded Anthony Tolliver, Kent Bazemore, a 2024 2nd round pick (POR), and a 2025 2nd round pick (POR) to the Kings for Trevor Ariza, Caleb Swanigan, and Wenyen Gabriel.
The Warriors traded Willie Cauley-Stein to the Mavericks for a 2020 2nd round pick (GSW).
The Magic traded Aaron Gordon and Terrence Ross to the Jazz for Rudy Gobert and Joe Ingles.
The Magic traded D.J. Augustin, Mohamed Bamba, a 2020 2nd round pick (LAL), and a 2021 2nd round pick (ORL) to the Timberwolves for Robert Covington.
The Magic traded B.J. Johnson, Michael Carter-Williams, Melvin Frazier, Khem Birch, Wes Iwundu, and a 2023 1st round pick (ORL) to the Thunder for Andre Roberson.
The Magic traded Nikola Vucevic to the Bulls for Otto Porter and Kris Dunn.
The Hawks traded Brandon Goodwin, Charles Brown, and a 2020 1st round pick (BKN) to the Knicks for Mitchell Robinson.
The Jazz traded Jordan Clarkson, Terrence Ross, a 2020 1st round pick (UTA), a 2023 2nd round pick (UTA), and a 2024 2nd round pick (UTA) to the Trailblazers for Carmelo Anthony and Hassan Whiteside.
The Jazz traded Mike Conley, a 2022 1st round pick (UTA), a 2022 2nd round pick (UTA), a 2024 1st round pick (UTA), and a 2025 2nd round pick (UTA) to the Pistons for Derrick Rose and Andre Drummond.
The Thunder traded Darius Bazley, Wes Iwundu, a 2023 1st round pick (OKC), and a 2026 1st round pick (LAC) to the Knicks for Kevin Knox.

The Jazz traded Ed Davis, Hassan Whiteside, Royce O'Neale, and Tony Bradley to the Timberwolves for Andrew Wiggins, Gorgui Dieng, a 2023 1st round pick (MIN), a 2025 1st round pick (MIN), a 2026 1st round pick (MIN), and a 2026 2nd round pick (MIN).

The Timberwolves traded D.J. Augustin, Ed Davis, Josh Okogie, Jordan Bell, and a 2020 2nd round pick (LAL) to the Pistons for Christian Wood, Langston Galloway, Sekou Doumbouya, Tim Frazier, and a 2024 1st round pick (UTA).
The Jazz traded Miye Oni to the Knicks for a 2020 2nd round pick (CHA).
The Magic traded Otto Porter and a 2022 1st round pick (ORL) to the Pelicans for Jrue Holiday.

The Trailblazers traded Damian Lillard to the Suns for Tyler Johnson, Frank Kaminsky, a 2020 1st round pick (MIL), a 2020 1st round pick (PHX), a 2020 2nd round pick (PHX), and a 2026 1st round pick (PHX).
The Rockets traded Michael Frazier and a 2021 2nd round pick (HOU) to the Bulls for Shaquille Harrison.

The Jazz traded a 2023 1st round pick (MIN), a 2023 1st round pick (UTA), a 2025 1st round pick (MIN), a 2026 1st round pick (MIN), a 2026 2nd round pick (MIN), and a 2026 2nd round pick (UTA) to the Timberwolves for nothing.
The Jazz traded a 2025 1st round pick (UTA) to the Timberwolves for nothing.
The Magic traded Amile Jefferson, Vic Law, a 2025 2nd round pick (ORL), a 2026 1st round pick (ORL), and a 2026 2nd round pick (ORL) to the Timberwolves for Noah Vonleh.
The Warriors traded D'Angelo Russell to the Heat for Justise Winslow, Meyers Leonard, and a 2022 2nd round pick (MIA).

The Warriors traded Stephen Curry to the Magic for Evan Fournier, Al-Farouq Aminu, Markelle Fultz, a 2020 2nd round pick (ORL), a 2021 1st round pick (ORL), a 2022 2nd round pick (ORL), a 2024 1st round pick (ORL), and a 2025 1st round pick (ORL).
The Warriors traded Klay Thompson and a 2025 2nd round pick (GSW) to the Celtics for Gordon Hayward and a 2020 2nd round pick (BOS).
